---
---

<section id="instalacion" class="py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-violet-600/5 rounded-full blur-[150px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Cómo <span class="text-gradient-animated">usarlo</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Un archivo. Cero configuración. Funciona al instante.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-1 group relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-violet-400 font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-colors">
            1
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Clona el repositorio</h3>
            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-sm text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-violet-400">git clone</span> https://github.com/Haplee/token-efficiency.git
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-2 group relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-violet-400 font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-colors">
            2
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Elige tu perfil</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-3">Copia el archivo que mejor se adapte a tu proyecto:</p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
              <div><span class="text-violet-400"># Universal</span></div>
              <div><span class="text-cyan-400">cp</span> token-efficiency/claude/CLAUDE.md ./tu-proyecto/</div>
              <div class="mt-2"><span class="text-violet-400"># Coding</span></div>
              <div><span class="text-cyan-400">cp</span> token-efficiency/claude/profiles/CLAUDE.coding.md ./tu-proyecto/CLAUDE.md</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-3 group relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-violet-400 font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-colors">
            3
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Listo</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Claude Code lee el archivo <code class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-400 rounded text-sm">CLAUDE.md</code> automáticamente. 
              Sin código, sin configuración extra. El comportamiento cambia al instante.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center animate-on-scroll delay-4">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 rounded-2xl">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-sm text-violet-300">
          Las instrucciones del usuario siempre priman sobre cualquier configuración
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="py-12 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        © 2026 Fran Vidal Mateo. MIT License.
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="https://github.com/Haplee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
